### Gap 2: Multi-Provider Support Incomplete
**Status**: ⚠️ PARTIAL  
**Severity**: P0  
**Architecture**: A7 (proposed), D40 (implemented)  
**Impact**: System locked to Anthropic Claude only; cannot leverage 5-tier optimization

